<!-- --><p>i&#x27;m guessing you want to know css specifically for <!-- --><em>goofing around on cohost<!-- --></em>, which makes it a little different.  several features are unavailable, several other features are only possible with creative trickery, and everything else is kind of an ugly mess<!-- --></p>
